A vintage 1920s art deco illustration of a magician's hands hovering over an ornate wooden box, from which streams of golden ribbons unfurl and transform into intricate mechanical blueprints and architectural diagrams floating in mid-air. The ribbons spiral upward in elegant curves, each one morphing from solid fabric into detailed technical drawings with gears, circuits, and flowing patterns. The color palette features deep burgundy, gold leaf, and midnight blue against a cream background. The composition has the symmetrical elegance of vintage magic show posters, with decorative geometric borders framing the scene. Dramatic spotlighting creates a sense of theatrical wonder and transformation.
